Theres so much to do and learn when you can get hands-on at a museum!

programme.title: Blippi

programme.title: Blippi

While hes there, he also gets to taste some delicious coconut water. Then, Blippi is back home exploring Tenino, Washington on a bicycle! He visits an outdoor play park, a fire station and more as he learns about being active and exploring the world around him!

programme.title: Blippi
programme.desc: Join Blippi as he becomes a baker for a day! Blippi visits his friend Lior the Baker to bake some tasty treats. programme.title: Mister Mayfair - A Song To Kill For
programme.desc: Max Mayfair has it all; a beautiful girlfriend, Ava, a new London crime family, and thanks to his latest heist, a priceless diamond necklace. However, when mafioso Calbones henchmen catch up with Mike and Armen, determined to drag them back to New York to pay for their crimes, Max has everything to lose. Teaming up with his old friend, Marseille Mafia crime boss, Paul, Max hatches a plan to lure the New York Mafia to Mayfair.

programme.title: Chosen Family
programme.desc: No information available

programme.title: Mister Mayfair - Serenas Game
programme.desc: Refusing to comply with Tommys demands, Max and Paul conspire to have the British gangster eliminated and Serena arrested. With Tommy dead and Serena in handcuffs, it appears as though Max has succeeded. His plan goes awry, however, when MI6 force Max to help Serena bring down her employers: the Russian mob. Torn between a life of crime with Serena or happiness with Ava, nothing is ever simple in the life of Max Mayfair.

programme.title: The Competition
programme.desc: No information available

programme.title: Clean
programme.desc: Tormented by his criminal past, Clean attempts a quiet life caring for his community and as a mentor to his young neighbor Dianda. When local gang violence puts his neighbors life in danger, Clean finds himself returning to his violent past.

programme.title: Broadcast
programme.desc: After a billionaire creates a drug called INOC which stops the aging process, the future of a world where death no longer exists is seen. The story of the fate of mankind is told while also revealing an elusive truth to its unknowing spectator.

programme.title: Blowback
programme.desc: After planning a perfect heist, Nick is ready to score. One problem, his girl and the crew, have other ideas. They take Nick down in a hail of bullets but Nick doesnt die and in a race for his life, seeks revenge one target at a time.

programme.title: Mayfair - Shooting Paul
programme.desc: Hoping to put the past behind him and go legit, Max is persuaded by Paul to open a new Mister Mayfair club in Portugal. Conflict, however, seems to follow Max wherever he goes. Drawn into a violent turf war between London Gangsters and the Italian Mafia, his relationship with Ava is jeopardised by the arrival of his former flame, Serena. Maxs carefully crafted world seems to be collapsing around him. With his familys lives on the line, Max is blackmailed by British crime boss, Tommy, to assassinate his best friend, Paul.

programme.title: Operation Sea Wolf
programme.desc: The German Navy and the last remaining U-Boats, were formed together for one last mission to attack the United States Homeland.

programme.title: Mister Mayfair - The Spyce Of Life
programme.desc: Returning from a romantic getaway with Ava, Max finds himself on the wrong side of the law yet again. Now blackmailed by MI6, Max must spy on two suspected terrorists; Aziz and Omar, who are regular customers at his club. Accompanied by his London crime family, Max breaks into Omars country estate and discovers his sinister plan. With everything on the line, Max must race to uncover a highly skilled hackers identity before its too late.

programme.title: American Sicario
programme.desc: Based on the true story, Edgar Valdez, drug lord and cartel leader, is betrayed by one of the brothers. Seeking retribution, Valdez will risk it all to gain control of the Feliz cartel.

programme.title: In Isolation
programme.desc: Four friends wanted to get away from it all in a remote country house but when a mysterious injured man turns up on their doorstep telling tales of a city ravaged by a epidemic and the looters who have pursued him, the friends rally to help.

programme.title: Altitude
programme.desc: A female FBI agent is offered millions to help a thief escape from a hijacked airplane.

programme.title: The Legion
programme.desc: Noreno, a half-Roman, is entrusted with the mission of crossing the snowy mountains of Armenia, swarming with Parthian patrols, to seek help for his slowly dying men.

programme.title: Mojave Diamonds
programme.desc: A former MMA fighter and his brothers must rescue their kidnapped family from a dangerous crime syndicate after $50M of illegal diamonds gets stolen.

programme.title: High Voltage
programme.desc: After a lightning strike kills the lead singer of a band, she is resurrected with electrifying special abilities.

programme.title: Johnny And Clyde
programme.desc: Johnny and Clyde are two serial killers who are on an endless crime spree. They decide to assemble a group of criminals and misfits to steal from Alanas casino and pull off the heist of the century.

programme.title: Locked In
programme.desc: A single mother must protect her daughter and herself during a heist gone wrong at a high-tech storage facility.

programme.title: A Tale Of Two Guns
programme.desc: A deputized gunslinger takes up the call to hunt down the last Cowboy, the chase is on and the bullets fly and only one of these hardened men can survive.

programme.title: Hideout
programme.desc: Evading police at a remote farmhouse after fumbling a robbery, four criminals discover that the family living there is not who they appear to be.

programme.title: Centigrade
programme.desc: A married couple find themselves trapped in their frozen vehicle after a blizzard and struggle to survive amid plunging temperatures and unforeseen obstacles.

programme.title: Rat Race
programme.desc: A Las Vegas casino magnate, determined to find a new avenue for wagering, sets up a race for money.

programme.title: Override
programme.desc: In 2040, a female humanoid A.I. is hacked by her husband and forced to kidnap the U.S. vice presidents son and execute him on live television.

programme.title: Project Legion
programme.desc: A young man trapped in his apartment with a swarm of demons outside his door must find a way to survive the night and escape from apartment 213.

programme.title: Crom
programme.desc: High school teenagers accidentally unleash an ancient Irish entity on their hometown and must stop it before midnight on Halloween.

programme.title: Broken Star
programme.desc: Abandoned by her friends and family and with her career in jeopardy, starlet Markey Marlowe is sequestered in a duplex with a reclusive landlord who just may be more dangerous than she is.

programme.title: Any Bullet Will Do
programme.desc: Two Brothers find themselves on opposing sides of the fight as one hopes to help abolish slavery while the other believes it is his God-given right.

programme.title: Come Out Fighting
programme.desc: During WWII, the American army have raced their way through the countryside on the border of France entering Nazi Germany. Hitler has deployed his secret weapon. Lieutenant Frank Ross encounters the Nazi weapon and an intense aerial battle ensues.

programme.desc: Join Rob and his friends for a day of mummies, wishes and making the grade! First, the crew travels to the Pyramid Planet to learn more about Pharaohs and Mummies, but Robs practical joke goes a little too far. Then, wishing they could all make a wish that would come true, the gang heads for the Wishing Planet. But they soon find that all their wishes backfire! Finally, the robots visit the Tune-Up Planet to get upgrades that will increase their abilities.

programme.title: Rob the Robot
programme.desc: Join Rob and his friends for a tricky picnic and a trip to the lost and found! The gang heads to the Comet Cake Planet for dessert, but theres only one cake left and a greedy alien robot steals it! Then, the crew goes to the Picnic Planet for a picnic, but their food begins to vanish into thin air! Finally, when Ema cant find her favorite moon boots, the crew departs for the Lost And Found Planet, but they all get lost in the giant piles of items!

programme.title: Little Baby Bum
programme.desc: Have a calming and magical night with Twinkle the star! When Bao Bao struggles to sleep, Twinkle arrives and transforms into a hot air balloon to lift her cot into the night sky so she can see the moon. Then, she helps Max, Muffin and Bao Bao get ready for bed by transforming into a cuddly teddy bear to give them all warm goodnight hugs. From creating a magical rainbow over the bath to turning into a kite for a gentle ride, Twinkle always makes bedtime magical.

programme.title: Little Baby Bum
programme.desc: Get ready for sweet dreams and bedtime songs! Mummy helps Mia begin her nighttime routine by tucking her toys into cozy spaces. Then, they try out some super simple and calming animal-related yoga poses to help Mia have a restful sleep. Daddy also shows Mia that routines can be fun with his brush your teeth dance! Finally, Mummy and Daddy play a beautiful lullaby on their guitars to help soothe the kids to sleep under the twinkling stars.

programme.title: Go Buster
programme.desc: Join Buster as he uses his brains to save the day! When he overloads the carwash with bubble mix, he gets trapped in a giant bubble and floats away! He has to use all his smarts to find a way back down. Then, when Amber the Ambulance crashes and cant move, theres a big emergency! Buster has to muster up his courage and become a Hero Ambulance Bus to save his best friend Scout from a broken bridge.

programme.title: Go Buster
programme.desc: Sometimes friends need a hero, and Buster is always ready to help! When he gets caught in a scary storm, he rushes to shelter, but then he spots his friend Scout, stuck in a muddy puddle! Buster has to muster all his courage to go back out and rescue her. But sometimes, even heroes need help! On another day, Buster gets stuck in the mud himself and has to be towed out by Terry Tractor. From stopping a runaway train to standing up to a bully, Buster is always there for his friends.

programme.title: Geckos Garage
programme.desc: Gecko and the Mechanicals face a big test of skill and teamwork! First, the Mechs are in Garage School when a real emergency comes in. In a role reversal, they must fix Fiona the Firetrucks starter motor while Gecko instructs them! Then, when Blue crashes during a flying race, Gecko must show his skill to repair him. The day ends with a big American football game where Gecko comes up with a clever strategy and a creative fix to help his team win!

programme.title: Geckos Garage
programme.desc: Grandma Gecko is here to help with some epic rescues! The action starts when Weasels accelerator gets stuck and he cant stop driving! Grandma Gecko and Gecko hop on a motorbike for a high-speed chase to save him. Then, when lots of vehicles get flat tires from nails on the road, Gecko feels the pressure and calls his Grandma to help him speedily change all the tires. From building a wind turbine to saving Blue, Grandma can do it all!

programme.title: Lellobee City Farm
programme.desc: Its time to sing, dance and play at Lellobee City Farm! The fun starts in the Boogie Barn where Grandma Mei teaches Ella, Rishi and all the cute animals a brand new alphabet song. Then, its time to get active as Mei leads a high-energy exercise dance for all the kids and animals! The day ends with a fun who can make the biggest splash? competition in the inflatable swimming pool, where even Pablo the pig and Heidi the horse join in!

programme.title: Lellobee City Farm
programme.desc: Its time to learn some healthy habits to keep you happy! First, Grandma Mei makes sure everyone washes their hands with lots of bubbles before eating some yummy dumplings. Then, when Baby Izzy doesnt want to eat her vegetables, Mei uses a bit of magic to make the veggies come to life to sing and dance! The healthy habits continue as the friends learn how to recycle trash to help save the planet and Ella learns to get right back up after getting a boo boo.

programme.title: Minibods
programme.desc: Its a day of learning to play together with blocks, dancing, football and storytime! First, Jeffs neat block towers keep getting knocked over by Bubbles, and they must learn to share their space. Then, Fuse refuses to listen to instructions during a dancing game and has to learn how to work as a team. The lessons continue as Bubbles learns not to cheat to win a football game and Jeff has to decide if he will share his new book during storytime.

programme.title: Minibods
programme.desc: Join the Minibods for an adventure with pedals, rescues and stars! Lulu goes camping but realizes shes left her favorite Binky Bunny behind and has to learn how to cope. Then, Newt goes on an adventure to find a real-life Flutterbug, but she has to be brave when her bikes stabilizers come off! The adventures continue as Jeff overcomes his fear of mud to rescue his feather duster and Bubbles builds a rocket to try and reach a big purple star in the sky!

programme.title: CoComelon Classroom
programme.desc: Join Ms. Appleberry and JJ for a learning adventure! Explore the letters B, C, R and U through fun activities. Play pretend as you make beep-beep sounds on a bus and act like a playful pup. Sing along to classic songs, discover surprises inside the Melon Learning Box with a special guest and enjoy a rainy day adventure.

programme.title: CoComelon
programme.desc: Join JJ for a nature walk and some of his favorite rhymes! First, JJs family shows him all the fun things we can do to help the Earth, like sorting trash for recycling. Then, the kids go on a nature walk with Bingo, collecting fun information in their scrapbooks! After the outdoor fun, its time for classic rhymes. Sing along as ten animal friends try to share a bed and help the three little kittens who have lost their mittens!

programme.title: JJs Animal Time
programme.desc: Join JJ and his animal friends on a big imagination adventure! First, Wally teaches everyone how to sail like real pirates, but theyll need to work together to stay on course! Then, when Mimi gets hungry, she decides the moon must be made of cheese, so the friends build a rocketship to fly there and find out! The adventure continues as they follow a treasure map to find special shape keys and help Little Red Riding JJ avoid Wally Wolfs silly traps in the woods.

programme.title: Lellobee City Farm
programme.desc: Get ready for some creative farm adventures with Ella! First, Ella brings school to Lellobee City Farm by creating a classroom in the Boogie Barn and teaching all her animal friends. Then, she helps Mei make some delicious jam using fresh strawberries, grapes and blueberries from the farm! The creative day ends with a magical night of stargazing, where Mei points out constellations that look just like the animals on the farm.

programme.title: Lellobee City Farm
programme.desc: Its a day of helping each other at Lellobee City Farm! When a mama songbirds eggs are about to hatch, Mei, Ella and Rishi build her a beautiful bird feeding table so she can take care of her new chicks. Then, when Heidi the Horse is feeling down in the dumps, Ella and all the friends put on a show and give her a big group hug to make her feel happy again! The helping continues as everyone learns the importance of sharing their veggies with a visiting gopher.

programme.title: Digley And Dazey
programme.desc: Join the crew for some fun competitions and a day of helping friends! First, the friends compete in a fun obstacle course to see who can finish the race the fastest and lift the special trophy! Then, just as the crew is ready to demolish an old building, a cute cat hops inside, and the team must rescue the kitten before finishing the job. The helping continues as they save another kitten from a dangerous situation and Dazey must think fast to save Mrs. Skip from a runaway river barge!

programme.title: Digley And Dazey
programme.desc: Get ready for playground games and construction fun! First, the crew has to build a crazy golf course! After they finish, they decide to try it out, but something goes wrong every time! Then, at the beach, Digley and Dazey challenge each other to a sandcastle competition. They each build castles that get bigger and sillier, and after some bickering, they decide to build one giant castle together! Plus, learn the alphabet and sing If Youre Happy and You Know It!

programme.title: KiiYii
programme.desc: Come sing your favorite classic songs with Kii and Yii! The sing-along starts on Old MacDonalds farm, where the friends learn how to spell the friendly dogs name in the song Bingo! Then, listen as Mr. Cat sings a story about his grand adventure visiting the Queen in her palace. The fun continues with the story of the Lion and the Unicorn, the flying adventure of Two Little Dicky Birds and a song about the Old Woman Who Lived in a Shoe.

programme.title: KiiYii
programme.desc: Get ready to learn about animals, numbers, ABCs and more! Join Kii and Yii as they head to Old MacDonalds farm to learn all the sounds the animals make. Then its time to learn numbers by singing along and counting the five cute penguins and five little ducks! The learning continues with a fun animal bus ride, a trip to space to sing Hey Diddle Diddle and an important lesson on how to cross the road carefully with a mother cat and her kitten.

programme.title: The Sharksons
programme.desc: Dive into some underwater learning adventures with The Sharksons! First, join the sea friends as they swim through the alphabet to learn their ABCs. Then, explore the vibrant hues of Splashy Reef with a journey to learn all the shades of a beautiful rainbow. The learning continues with important daily routines! Sing along with Tucker the Turtle as he takes a bath and watch as Baby Grub eagerly learns the importance of dental care by brushing her big, sharp shark teeth!

programme.title: The Sharksons
programme.desc: Join the Shark Family as they work hard to keep the sea clean! Its a busy day with so much rubbish on the seabed. Stanley Shark becomes his heroic alter-ego, Super Shark, to show everyone how to clean up and recycle properly! The Sharksons show their creativity by using recycled materials to build an amazing underwater ball pit and slide. Plus, see them use teamwork to operate little digger trucks and even fix a broken bus wheel using a sunken bin lid!

programme.title: Playtime With Twinkle
programme.desc: Its time to learn all about colors, shapes and numbers with Twinkle! First, learn how to count with Twinkle as she finds five balloons in the colors red, blue, green, yellow and purple! Then, join Twinkle and Sandy the Seagull to make sandcastles, learning different shapes like squares, triangles and circles. The learning continues as Twinkle and her friends build and count a beautiful tower of rainbow stones and discover the variety of shapes that clouds can take in the sky!

programme.title: Ninas Familia
programme.desc: Spend a fun-filled day with Nina and her amazing family! First, Nina and her siblings learn all about how things fly as they dream of soaring through the sky like their dad, who is a pilot! Then, its time for a yummy adventure in the kitchen as Nina and her Abuelita (grandma) decide to make a traditional Mexican breakfast for everyone. The family fun continues as they go on a scavenger hunt for colorful flowers and work together to help the magical Star Star get back into the sky!

programme.title: Dance Party
programme.desc: Its a dance party featuring all your favorite classic rhymes! Join JJ, Bella and Cece as they dance to Hey Diddle Diddle while the cow jumps over the moon. The fun continues as they help their friend Humpty Dumpty get home after a great fall with the help of some sea creature friends! Then, get ready to rock out with a band of monkeys in a brand-new version of Rockabye Baby. From Five Little Speckled Frogs to Looby Loo, its a dance party full of classic fun!

programme.title: CoComelon
programme.desc: Join JJ and his friends for a fun school day at Melon Patch Academy! Ms. Appleberry finds exciting ways to learn, like using building blocks and drawings to practice the alphabet. Then, the kids play a fun guessing game to learn all about the five senses and how to sign them in ASL! The learning continues as they sing about the days of the week, play a fun alphabet photo game on a rainy day and enjoy story time with the whole family. Its a day packed with learning and fun!

programme.title: Minibods
programme.desc: The Minibods are having a day of drawing, painting, music and a quick fix! Newt is drawing a beautiful flower but keeps rushing and crumpling her drawings, so she must learn to slow down. Then, when the Minibods help her finish a huge painting, Newt wants it all for herself! The creative chaos continues as Lulu struggles to make a music video with a marching Oddbird and Bubbles accidentally makes a mess while trying to fix a book dispenser.

programme.title: Minibods
programme.desc: Its a day of learning lessons at parties and games! Pogo is invited to Jeffs party, but Pogo wants it to be energetic while Jeff wants it to be calm, so they must learn to compromise. Then, Newt is desperate to win a gold star at Fuses gym challenges, but she keeps losing! She has to learn to persevere and not give up. The lessons continue as Lulu learns to wait her turn at a funfair and Fuse finds the courage to eat his healthy greens.

programme.title: Geckos Garage
programme.desc: Gecko is using his genius for some amazing outdoor fixes! On a rainy camping trip, Green Mechanical runs out of battery, so Gecko and Grandma create a water wheel from scratch to recharge her with green energy! Then, when Mr. Weasels advertising blimp starts to fly away with him attached, Gecko must use a bouncy castle to prepare a soft landing! From finding lost keys in a sandcastle to stopping Max from getting stuck in the mud, Gecko can fix it all!

programme.title: Geckos Garage
programme.desc: Get ready for game day goofs and Grandmas amazing fixes! The fun starts with a basketball game, but when Max the Monster Truck tries a slam dunk, he breaks his suspension and gets a teddy bear stuck in the hoop! Then, when Gecko gets a boo boo while trying to fix Bobby the Buss mixed-up controls, Grandma Gecko arrives just in time to help with the repair. The day ends with Grandmas own goof, as she starts sleepwalking during a sleepover!

programme.title: Lellobee City Farm
programme.desc: Get ready for some creative farm adventures with Ella! First, Ella brings school to Lellobee City Farm by creating a classroom in the Boogie Barn and teaching all her animal friends. Then, she helps Mei make some delicious jam using fresh strawberries, grapes and blueberries from the farm! The creative day ends with a magical night of stargazing, where Mei points out constellations that look just like the animals on the farm.

programme.title: Lellobee City Farm
programme.desc: Its time to learn some healthy habits to keep you happy! First, Grandma Mei makes sure everyone washes their hands with lots of bubbles before eating some yummy dumplings. Then, when Baby Izzy doesnt want to eat her vegetables, Mei uses a bit of magic to make the veggies come to life to sing and dance! The healthy habits continue as the friends learn how to recycle trash to help save the planet and Ella learns to get right back up after getting a boo boo.

programme.title: Family Spy
programme.desc: Ep02 Roz cuba menenangkan Indah yang risaukan Rin dan Daniel yang telah mulakan penyiasatan. Namun Daniel tidak mahu mendengar nasihat ibunya, Roz. Daniel dan Roz menggunakan cara berbeza untuk mencari Rin. Pihak polis menerima rakaman pesanan suara Rin.

programme.title: #Tom Tom Bak Series
programme.desc: Datuk Aznil Haji Nawawi turun padang sempena pencarian bakat baru #TomTomBak. Ramai yang hadir untuk menonjolkan bakat yang mereka ada. Bermacam ragam And aksi lucu dapat kita saksikan. Anak-anak yang petah berborak juga turut dicari untuk musim terbaru ini.

programme.title: Geng Gajet
programme.desc: Perniagaan Kedai Bob semakin merosot dan Geng memutuskan untuk merancang And membina kedai dalam talian yang akhirnya memperoleh kejayaan! Namun, masalah berlaku apabila pemilik kedai pesaing menggoda Hafiz dengan perjanjian yang akan mengkhianati rakan-rakannya.

programme.desc: The Call duck is a domestic duck species native to the Netherlands. Males can weigh about 570 to 680 grams. Because its call is different from other ducks, Call Ducks were bred as hunting ducks, now most of them are used as pets. They mainly live in the Netherlands, Japan, and Southeast Asia. They were introduced to the pet market in recent years and were originally used by European hunters to lure wild ducks using their call. Their ducklings are described as having fair skin, big breasts and round butts. They can heal peoples moods, and their cute appearance adds joy.

programme.title: Cute Pets At Home
programme.desc: Ali the elephant at Shoushan Zoo, carries the childhood memories of many children, both young and old. Although he is now 49 years old, he is still energetic under the care of the keepers. Once the new zoo is completed, the public will be able to see Ali again. When the caregiver helps Ali take a shower, Ali will take the opportunity to replenish his body with water; sometimes he will step on water in the pool and use his nose to enjoy the fun of playing in the water. nThere are currently only three African elephants in Taiwan. In addition to Ali, the other two are in the Taipei City Zoo. Because African elephants are endangered wild animals, their import and export are strictly controlled. If these three elephants die in the future, Taiwan may no longer see any African elephants. Shoushan Zoo vows to take good care of Ali so that Alis heartwarming story can continue, and shoulder the mission of life education, so that everyones visit to the Shoushan Zoo is the starting point of happy memories. In addition to Ali the elephant, Shoushan Zoo currently has two white rhinos, male Xiqi from the Taipei City Zoo and female Baby who was bred naturally in the zoo. nWhite rhino Xiqi was loaned to Shoushan Zoo in hope that he could successfully mate with the female white rhino Baby to raise the white rhino population.

programme.title: Cute Pets At Home
programme.desc: The white cockatoo is one of the more common macaw species, but its number in the wild has gradually declined in recent years. Hand-reared white cockatoos love to be close to their owners. Their large size is one of their features. Like other large macaws, white cockatoos are really loud, but if its a hand-reared bird raised from a young age, the situation of screaming will be much better. If you want to raise a pair of adult birds, it is ideal to keep them in an open area with good sound insulation or without neighbors. Their friendly personalities make them one of the more suitable large macaw species as pets.

Victoria se conmueve al ver a Nicols bajo la lluvia esperando que ella le de una respuesta; Clementina insta a su amiga a no ceder todava. Eugenia se molesta al leer la nota que le envio Yosmir con el libro que le regalo sugiriendole que, cuando vuelva a ir a la cancha de bateo, lleve a su mam con ella. Nicols le deja un mensaje en el celular a Fernanda pidiendole que no salga de su casa, pues no saben que quiere la persona que la est amenazando y el no se perdonara que le pase algo por no haberla detenido a tiempo en su plan.

programme.title: Piel Salvaje - S01:E44
programme.desc: Marcelina visita a la Madre Isabel para hablarle sobre su relacion con Rosa Blanco, quien fue su mejor amiga y ella la traiciono; por eso quiere impedir su regreso.

programme.title: Piel Salvaje - S01:E45
programme.desc: Ante una llamada telefonica de Rosa Blanco a Luciano, Camila, ilusionada, quiere hablar con su mam. El Capitn Torrealba la ayude a entender los secretos que existen sobre el crimen. Ante la brutal agresion a Sebastin, Ezequiel quiere vengarla con Fernando, un Aragon.

programme.title: El Desprecio - S01:E63
programme.desc: Una firme sor Juana busca a Pastora para conversar, Lara Portillo acepta con interes su propuesta.

programme.title: El Desprecio - S01:E64
programme.desc: Pastora interroga con saa a Elisenda, quien llora desconsolada; desea saber quien es la mujer realmente.

programme.title: Corazon Traicionado - S01:E63
programme.desc: Lorena en shock ante el cuerpo sin vida de su comadre y amiga. Pedro, fro, la obliga a verlo a los ojos y le advierte que con un sicario no se juega; que la proxima vez que se le ocurra traicionarlo, la vctima ser su hijo. El Juez Montilla afirma que dependiendo de lo que se discuta y los acuerdos a los que lleguen en esa audiencia, podr revocar o no la libertad bajo fianza de Isabel.

programme.title: Te Tengo en Salsa - S01:E61
programme.desc: Adriana se encuentra con Cristian. Pero es Cesar quien la est esperando. Cristian se acerca al lugar y se paraliza al ver que es su hermano gemelo quien conversa con la muchacha.

programme.desc: Cesar se presenta en casa de los Perroni. Cristian, frente a todos, comienza a insultarlo y sufre un infarto que le quita la vida. Azalea culpa a Adriana de lo ocurrido..

programme.title: La Trepadora - S01:E026
programme.desc: Victoria y Nicols se besan enamorados; el le promete que siempre estar a su lado antes de sumergirse con ella en el mar en medio de un apasionado beso. Antonieta y Eugenia exigen a Leopoldo les diga que est ocurriendo con Fernanda que no ha aparecido desde temprano. Hilario disfruta la velada con Florencia en un parque de diversiones donde la joven lo abraza y asegura saber que el la va a proteger siempre; mientas que, internamente, contiene la rabia que siente por el hombre. Hansen siente cierta decepcion cuando Adelaida sugiere que lo quiere como un hermano y confa en que el no sera capaz de ocultarle algo que le hiciera dao. Carlos est a punto de confesarle su amor a la mujer, pero desiste cuando ella le habla de que su nico sueo es que su amor por Hilario convierta su matrimonio en algo distinto a lo que es actualmente.

programme.title: The New Frontier - S01:E01 - From There to Here

programme.title: Carters W.A.R. - S02:E08 - The Forgotten Giants
programme.desc: No toda la caza furtiva es por cuernos y colmillos. En muchas partes de frica, asolada por la pobreza, las jirafas son asesinadas sin piedad por su carne. programme.desc: So far this season there have been 11 Grands Prix, and now just one remains: the Mubadala Abu Dhabi Sail Grand Prix 2025 Season Grand Final, presented by Abu Dhabi Sports Council. All 12 teams will be in action in Abu Dhabi, facing off in six electrifying fleet races split over two days.nnFor fans, the Grand Final is the ultimate thrill ride. Every tack, gybe and pass could decide who lifts the SailGP trophy. Its not just a race - its the pinnacle of SailGP, a clash of titans, and the perfect end to a season of world-class competition.
